NightFood Holdings, Inc. Key Developments

NightFood Holdings, Inc. announced delayed 10-Q filing
May 16 17
On 05/16/2017, NightFood Holdings, Inc. announced that they will be unable to file their next 10-Q by the deadline required by the SEC.


NightFood Seeks Acquisitions
May 4 17
Sean Folkson, Chief Executive Officer of NightFood Holdings, Inc. (OTCPK:NGTF) stated that in conjunction with the $5 million Equity Purchase Agreement and the move up to the Quote  Board, provides  the company access to capital resources necessary for the growth of the NightFood brand and for possible merger and acquisition opportunities.


NightFood Holdings, Inc. announced delayed 10-Q filing
Feb 15 17
On 02/15/2017, NightFood Holdings, Inc. announced that they will be unable to file their next 10-Q by the deadline required by the SEC.


