			Company Description 


			NightFood Holdings, Inc. operates as a holding company, which through its subsidiary engages in nutritional food development, marketing and distribution business. It manufactures markets and distributes a functional food line of snacks that are suitable for evening consumption. The company was found...
		


                NightFood Holdings, Inc. operates as a holding company, which through its subsidiary engages in nutritional food development, marketing and distribution business. It manufactures markets and distributes a functional food line of snacks that are suitable for evening consumption. The company was founded on October 16, 2013 and is headquartered in Tarrytown, NY.
            




